             were indicted for <rs id="t18301209-208-off1160" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18301209-208-off1160" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18301209-208-off1160" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18301209-208-cd1161" type="crimeDate">16th of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-208-off1160 t18301209-208-cd1161"></join>, 1 pair of shoes, value 8s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18301209-208-victim1792" type="victimName">
                           Ralph 
                           Wilcoxon
                        <interp inst="t18301209-208-victim1792" type="surname" value="Wilcoxon"></interp>
